湖北：继续实施严格的离汉离鄂通道管控措施。
Hubei: We will continue to implement strict control measures for the exit channel from Han to Hubei.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
湖北省人民政府湖北省人民政府网站3月11日消息，为统筹推进疫情防控和经济社会发展工作，加快建立同疫情防控相适应的经济社会运行秩序，根据《中华人民共和国突发事件应对法》《中华人民共和国传染病防治法》和湖北省重大突发公共卫生事件I级响应机制等有关规定，现就有序推进企业复工复产和人员省内安全流动等事项通告如下：一、分区分级分类分时有序推进企业复工复产全省以县域为单位，划分低、中、高风险区，实施分区分级差异化防控，企业分类分时有条件复工复产，具体行业企业实行灵活动态管理。
In order to promote the prevention and control of epidemic diseases and promote the establishment of an economic and social operational order compatible with the prevention and control of epidemic diseases, the work of enterprises is now divided into low, medium and high risk areas based on county level.
（一）武汉市企业复工复产安排：涉及保障疫情防控必需（医疗器械、检验检测仪器设备、药品、防护品、消杀用品生产销售以及原材料配套等）、公共事业运行必需（供水、供电、供热、油气、通讯、环卫、医废处理等）、群众生活必需（蔬菜水果生产经营，粮油食品、肉蛋奶、水产品生产加工和销售，超市卖场、母婴用品销售、农副产品批发、快递物流、周转仓储、电商、配送制餐饮等）、农业生产必需（种子种苗生产、畜禽水产养殖和茶叶加工、饲料加工、磷复肥化肥农膜农药兽药生产和销售、农机生产与服务等相关企业及合作社）以及其他涉及重要国计民生的企业可以复工复产。
(1) Arrangements for resumption of production by enterprises in Wuhan city: Enterprises and cooperatives concerned with ensuring epidemic prevention and control of epidemic diseases (medical equipment, inspection and testing equipment, medicines, protective products, disinfectant production and marketing, raw materials), necessities for public use (water, electricity, heat, oil and gas, communications, meat and egg milk, aquatic products, feed processing,
对全国、全球产业链配套有重大影响的企业，在防控措施到位、防控责任落实的前提下，按程序批准后可以复工复产。
Enterprises that have a significant impact on the support of national and global industrial chains may resume production upon approval of the relevant procedures, provided that control measures are in place and the responsibility for prevention and control is fulfilled.
春节以来未停工停业的企业可以继续生产。
Enterprises that have not stopped operating since the Spring Festival may continue to produce.
其他企业先按不早于3月20日24时前复工复产。
Others resumed work before 2400 hours on or before 20 March.
（二）武汉市以外其他高风险地区企业复工复产安排：涉及保障疫情防控、公共事业运行、群众生活、农业生产必需以及其他涉及重要国计民生的企业，金融保险、港口和货运站场、重点产业链配套企业，承担国家、省市重大工程和重点项目的企业等，可以有序复工复产。
(2) Arrangements for the resumption of production by enterprises in high-risk areas other than Wuhan may resume work in an orderly manner: enterprises involved in ensuring the prevention and control of epidemic diseases, the operation of public services, people's lives, agricultural production and other enterprises that involve important national livelihood, financial insurance, ports and freight yards and key industry chains.
春节以来未停工停业的企业可以继续生产。
Enterprises that have not stopped operating since the Spring Festival may continue to produce.
（三）中风险地区企业复工复产安排：除上述类型企业可以复工复产或继续生产外，用工和产业链配套以本地为主的工业、农业产业化企业，以室外作业为主的建筑业企业，法律会计、软件信息服务等相关服务业企业，可以有序复工复产。
Arrangements for the resumption of production by enterprises in medium-risk areas: In addition to the enterprises of the above-mentioned categories that can resume production or continue production, enterprises engaged in industry and industrial chain supporting mainly local industries and agricultural industrialization, construction enterprises mainly engaged in outdoor work, and relevant service enterprises such as legal accounting and software information services may resume production in an orderly manner.
（四）低风险地区企业复工复产安排：实行限制清单管理，不在限制清单内的市场主体可以有序复工复产或继续生产。
Arrangements for the resumption of production by enterprises in low-risk areas: The management of restricted lists shall be implemented so that the market subjects who are not on the restricted list may resume production or resume production in an orderly manner.
限制清单内的市场主体，主要包括人员聚集度高、场所相对密闭的影剧院、棋牌室、游艺厅、书店、网吧、舞厅、酒吧、KTV、公共浴室、足浴店、美容店、健身房、培训机构、堂食类餐饮等，疫情解除前不得复工复产。
The main bodies of the market in the restricted list include theaters, chess rooms, recreation halls, bookstores, Internet cafes, dance halls, bars, KTV, public bathrooms, foot baths, beauty parlors, gymnasiums, training institutions and restaurants.
企业复工复产前，应制定疫情防控工作方案和应急处置预案，做好相关准备工作，确保做到防控机制、员工排查、设施物资、环境消杀、安全生产“五个到位”。
When an enterprise returns to work, it shall work out an epidemic prevention and control programme and a plan for emergency treatment, and make appropriate preparations to ensure that the prevention and control mechanism, staff clearance, facilities and materials, environmental sterilization and production safety are "five in place."
企业复工复产由所在县（市）新冠肺炎疫情防控指挥部（以下简称指挥部）负责审批，市辖区企业复工复产由所在市指挥部负责审批。
The re-establishment of industrial production shall be examined and approved by the New Crown Pneumonia Control Command of the county (city) where the enterprise is located (hereinafter referred to as the Command).
二、推进人员安全有序流动（一）继续实施严格的离汉离鄂通道管控措施，做好滞留在鄂外地人员服务保障工作。
Promoting the safe and orderly flow of personnel （ 1 ） Continue to implement strict control measures over the passage from the Han to the Hubei ， and do a good job of ensuring the service of the personnel stranded in the field.
（二）中风险、低风险地区人员，凭健康码“绿码”，在省内安全有序流动。
(2) Safe and orderly flow of personnel in medium-risk and low-risk areas within the province by virtue of the health code "green code."
武汉市以及省内其他高风险地区人员，凭健康码“绿码”，可与省内流入地采取“点对点”运输方式安全有序流动。
Wuhan city and other high-risk areas in the province, with the health code "green code", and the province can take the "point-to-point" transportation mode of safe and orderly flow.
（三）武汉市以外地区，在做好健康管理、落实防控措施的前提下，采取“点对点、一站式”的办法，集中精准输送务工人员安全返岗，帮助外地滞留在鄂人员安全有序返乡。
(3) Outside Wuhan city, on the premise of doing a good job in health management and implementing prevention and control measures, adopt a "point-to-point, one-stop-shop" approach, and concentrate on the safe and orderly return of migrant workers to their places of origin so as to help them return home safely and orderly.
（四）各级指挥部做好滞留在外人员安全有序返鄂服务保障工作，将返鄂人员纳入本地疫情防控管理。
4) Headquarters at all levels shall ensure the safe and orderly return of personnel to their places of origin, and bring returned personnel into the management of local disease prevention and control.
三、加强交通运输管理（一）中风险、低风险地区的省内客运航班、旅客列车、客运汽车、客轮以及城市公交，在采取必要防控措施的前提下，逐步有序恢复。
Strengthening Transportation Management （ 1 ） Stepwise and orderly recovery of passenger flights, passenger trains, passenger cars, passenger ships and urban buses in risk and low-risk areas under the premise of taking necessary control measures.
（二）武汉市以及省内其他高风险地区的客运航班、旅客列车、客运汽车、客轮以及城市公交继续停运。
(2) Passenger and passenger flights, passenger trains, passenger cars, passenger ships and city buses continue to be suspended in Wuhan and other high-risk areas of the province.
四、继续延迟学校开学省内大专院校、中小学、中职学校、技工院校、幼儿园等继续延期开学。
IV. Continuing delays in the opening of schools in the provinces colleges, schools, secondary vocational schools, technical colleges, kindergartens, etc. continue to delay the opening of schools.
具体开学时间根据疫情防控情况，经科学评估后确定。
Specific school start time according to the situation of disease prevention and control, after scientific assessment.
五、严格落实各方责任各地各部门要按照“坚定信心、同舟共济、科学防治、精准施策”的总要求，持续用力加强疫情防控工作，精准有序扎实推动复工复产，做好群众生活和企业复工复产的各项服务保障，确保社会大局平稳有序。
Strictly Carrying Out the Responsibilities of All Parties In accordance with the overall requirements of "firm confidence, working together in this boat, scientific prevention and treatment, and accurate and accurate policy-making," departments everywhere should work hard to strengthen prevention and control of the epidemic, promote resumption of production in an accurate and orderly manner, and ensure a smooth and orderly return to work.
复工复产企业要认真履行疫情防控主体责任，严格落实疫情防控各项措施，严防疫情发生，维护员工身体健康，确保生产经营安全有序。
Enterprises that resume production should earnestly fulfill their main responsibilities of disease prevention and control, strictly implement measures to prevent the outbreak of epidemic diseases, safeguard the health of employees and ensure safe and orderly production and management.
希望广大人民群众继续理解、支持、配合疫情防控工作，凝心聚力、众志成城，合力打赢疫情防控的人民战争、总体战、阻击战，力争全省经济社会发展早日全面步入正常轨道。
We hope that the masses of the people will continue to understand, support and cooperate in the prevention and control of the epidemic, and concentrate their efforts on winning the people's war, the general war and the fight against the disease.
湖北省新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情防控指挥部2020年3月11日本期编辑邢潭推荐阅读。
Hubei Province new coronavirus infection pneumonia epidemic prevention and control command of March 11, 2020 issue editor Xingtan recommended reading.
